Text: It says 0 seeders, but I'm definitely seeding, and will continue doing so. Enjoy, this album is fantastic.

I've got the album on pre-order and it should be delivered today, but I couldn't resist the opportunity to hear this a little early. The songs are fantastic and the audio quality is more than adequate. Many thanks to the uploader! If you guys are able, please try to support Toh Kay, as well as Streetlight.
